GSD Core is a context-engineering and spec-driven development framework distributed
under the MIT License. GSD Master re-implements the GSD Core phase-loop conceptual
model (Discuss → Plan → Execute → Verify → Ship) with a different process shape
optimized for multi-plan orchestration, strict pre-flight validation, and autonomous
PR review. It is not a fork of the GSD Core source code.

